        <abstract> 
<p>Pleased with sum the reprint [of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>] has produced. Terms of payment accepted.</p>  
<p>Thanks JM for <hi rend="italic">Nonconformist</hi> [review of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>, 32 (1871): 240–1].</p> 
            <p>Would like to see other out-of-way reviews – especially religious.</p> 
<p>Other reviews favourable, including Wallace’s [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">7569</hi>], which is admirable.</p> 
        </abstract>
